gonna die, you actually wake up.

12:09.195 --> 12:12.599
So what it took was it took the
support of my friends, my family,

12:12.699 --> 12:15.802
and, you know, especially I got to
give credit where credit is due.

12:15.902 --> 12:18.171
Martin, you guys,
helped me out so much,

12:18.271 --> 12:21.574
