13:51.798 --> 13:53.233
That's why I love
that dude, you know,

13:53.333 --> 13:56.502
and, in turn, sometimes
I got to check Martin.

13:56.602 --> 13:57.906
Yeah.

13:59.972 --> 14:01.674
Believe me, you guys.

14:01.774 --> 14:04.010
It goes both ways.
Sometimes I have to check him.

14:04.110 --> 14:07.513
Not about his weight, but he
has his demons, too, you know.

14:07.613 --> 14:09.182
Oh, believe that. Yes.

