01:10:36.566 --> 01:10:38.801
I'm ironing the shirt, and I'm
talking to him about his grades.

01:10:38.901 --> 01:10:40.503
As I'm talking to him
about his grades,

01:10:40.603 --> 01:10:42.238
there's a car driving
in front of the house,

01:10:42.338 --> 01:10:43.473
and the stereo was really loud,

01:10:43.573 --> 01:10:45.241
